<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Iptables on Pan Binghong's Tech Blog</title><link>https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/tags/iptables/</link><description>Recent content in Iptables on Pan Binghong's Tech Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- 0.147.0</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 04:17:50 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/tags/iptables/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Iptables Common commands</title><link>https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/devops/iptables-common-commands/</link><pubDate>Wed, 12 Mar 2025 05:46:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/devops/iptables-common-commands/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>💡 iptables 全称为：netfilter/iptables 是一个IP数据包过滤系统。&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="iptables工作流程">iptables工作流程&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>采用数据包过滤机制工作的，所以它会对请求的数据包的包头进行分析，并根据我们预先设定的规则进行匹配来决定是否可以进入主机。&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>防火墙是一层一层过滤的。实际是按照配置规则的顺序从上到下，从前到后进行filter。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>如果匹配上规则，表明阻止还是通过，此时数据包就不再向下匹配新规则。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>如果规则中，没有表明阻止还是通过，即等同于没有匹配上规则，按照默认策略处理。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>防火墙的默认规则是对应的链的所有规则执行完成后才会执行。
&lt;img loading="lazy" src="https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/fc187c04-cf34-444f-b5f2-bdcdfad76660/5da2e1eb-c9ee-47d7-8b26-5710b6c7fa13/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&amp;X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&amp;X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466SFAEQDEM%2F20260416%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&amp;X-Amz-Date=20260416T041727Z&amp;X-Amz-Expires=3600&amp;X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEOz%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCIB%2F7UQegvsRe0%2BBVWvhP41qcExVy3J%2FQCl14AkS38fEmAiBSApfY2iKGdYT4TyubXJpUrwOPXCAzhQ34HQf6AVQrPyqIBAi1%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F8BEAAaDDYzNzQyMzE4MzgwNSIM5ZClIyhWtlDR4k7xKtwDADoyhzVflSQW1hfbxk6XTfFTrSDR%2BwRrRziN2Yt4EiQjvU4Ah9P1fD5ODylHjs4JkkyZ87BMY7l%2BRQfikPHy%2FEmPK78p4RPZFsESBe8WuEWa8Xx3yaBIeQd4tDO8QNAlpGn49sQTfv%2BILs0Gqr1pYX116qPXAJ6uqK2TqEcNkAA9TUKX3YqoKUoRq%2FwmdfPXqdS8HeURrBd0%2FEc3vCXLWMCY0kHSq5XFvktaSfd75IQ8W135DMHc%2FUzK%2FiX9JMI83OIi3l289daB0oLh08yaex9YjKI2%2BYNthTqtA8NF58x5mc%2FiBsQK9IhR1xUS0MZLDqdeOl95xpYYnAKAF94h44WZ%2BBL0IV%2BGUbRzvDfBcVQi8O0PuxZ3QAFFsY9porzWclcPhCzOjX3L91iK7YH%2BlKDyJHYG09v1k5K1W3S%2BUjsr8Qp9NdlPiZwEVb8gnnVzu3PDmzbfJCTpEyZh3pqqZ8OuzTu%2BhLaFjDB1GGWekfexEQu6IuE86RiOWebJ8TrUgBX7znXQWw9nUygVPpG8N96au0lpcVWnxm0WjyIq61EItXVjuDvftjTW9OMLQqtDALUWWE1mLnCyk1n1xc9Yq9PhiSQoBZYuuuX%2FaAXUosdIDHeX%2FGUu8dhN6PUwwbWBzwY6pgFFWQDQWdd74j8RW1mfRZY4mkJvnLcZubfWQkMOuslsACAVQl5s7Gg9Tf%2BQFC85y8RtgWDFYgl8FTvLB7Nqvr0nU8E637%2BXhjmbbvB%2F72GBnU75HQnC%2FWk89IoXaqZ5Ecm0r1moXE%2BMocd9bRF3pq9fU1ezoOVlxExB4zNP6uDuR072gHnjPNnjknS6otJEkXdD11sY41E27LKEur9hceConzkb5i0%2B&amp;X-Amz-Signature=b930080031199b6412b50c51a555aac2e8c4077adbab79b844dc0fbb64fab3a5&amp;X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&amp;x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&amp;x-id=GetObject">&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
